Html:
What is the benefit of IoC container in MVVM Light? What is the benefit of the ViewModelLocator? Why not instantiating the view-models directly in the XAML file like below:<br />
<pre><code>&lt;UserControl&gt;
    &lt;UserControl.DataContext&gt;
        &lt;vm:MainViewModel/&gt;
    &lt;/UserControl.DataContext&gt;

    &lt;!-- Other user control elements here --&gt;

&lt;/UserControl&gt;</code></pre>
